title: Najadacze.pl
typeOfFood: Vegan, Indian, International, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Polish
description: Vegan restaurant offering a mix of cuisines inspired by world regions, from Poland to India. Sample menu items such as pierogi and samosa, falafel wraps and tofu curry over basmati rice. There are also cakes, smoothies, fresh juices, and coffee. Gluten-free options. Casual and cozy with free Wi-Fi. Service is quick. Affiliated with Ahimsa restaurant in Wroclaw.
